OL,3,CMan who called police on himself
OL,4,Cwanted to go back to prison
OL,6,FA 53-year-old homeless man in Guernsey
OL,7,Fwent on a shoplifting spree to
OL,8,Fpurposely get himself sent back to
OL,9,Fprison.
OL,11,FJason Crowther had only been out of
OL,12,FLes Nicolles for two weeks before
OL,13,Fgoing to two supermarkets to steal a
OL,14,Fpack of cheese slices, ham, cooked
OL,15,Fchicken breast and beer.
OL,17,FThis took place over the course of two
OL,18,Fdays in January and he then called the
OL,19,Fpolice on himself.
