OL,3,CMan who called police on himself
OL,4,Cwanted to go back to prison
OL,6,FHis advocate told the court that
OL,7,FCrowther had stolen the food and drink
OL,8,Fbecause he was hungry and had no
OL,9,Fmoney. He also said that he would
OL,10,Frather be back in prison because it
OL,11,Fwas 'safer'.
OL,13,FCrowther claimed that he didn't get
OL,14,Fenough support after being released
OL,15,Fand a lack of proper housing was
OL,16,Fimpacting his mental health. He was
OL,17,Falso dealing with the death of a
OL,18,Frelative.
