OL,3,CMan who called police on himself
OL,4,Cwanted to go back to prison
OL,6,FHe said he didn't want to be in the
OL,7,Fcommunity, just wanted stable
OL,8,Faccommodation and to live a law
OL,9,Fabiding life.
OL,11,FJudge Marc Davies said he had sympathy
OL,12,Ffor Crowther but there is help
OL,13,Favailable if he wanted it. It was up
OL,14,Fto him to take advantage of the
OL,15,Fsupport offered.
OL,17,FHe was sentenced to six months in
OL,18,Fprison, to start from when he was
OL,19,Ffirst arrested on the 19th of January.
