OL,3,CMan who called police on himself
OL,4,Cwanted to go back to prison
OL,6,FGuernsey's Home Affairs Committee was
OL,7,Fapproached for comment on the support
OL,8,Favailable for ex-offenders, however a
OL,9,Fcomment hasn't been provided yet.
OL,11,FOn the States of Guernsey website
OL,12,Fthere is a list of what support is
OL,13,Favailable to former inmates on
OL,14,Frelease, including:
OL,16,F- Referrals to social housing
OL,18,F- An offender deposit assistance scheme
OL,20,F- Access to emergency or temporary
OL,21,Faccommodation
